trans-unit.source: May be ANNO_THIS, indicating that the annotation affects the indicated accessible element only; or ANNO_CONTAINER, indicating that it applies to the element and its immediate element children.
trans-unit.target: 可以是 ANNO_THIS，表示附註只會影響指定的可存取項目，或者為 ANNO_CONTAINER，表示附註會套用到項目與其直接子項目。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Accessibility.CAccPropServicesClass" /> and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) <see langword="IAccPropServices" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Accessibility.CAccPropServicesClass" /> 和其所有公開的成員都是元件物件模型 (COM) <see langword="IAccPropServices" /> 介面之 Managed 包裝函式的一部分。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the [Microsoft Active Accessibility](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/dd373592(v=vs.85).aspx) documentation.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[Microsoft Active Accessibility](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/dd373592(v=vs.85).aspx)文件。

trans-unit.source: Identifies the accessible element that is to be annotated.
trans-unit.target: 識別要標註的可存取項目。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the length of the string identified by the <c>pIDString</c> parameter.
trans-unit.target: 指定由 <c>pIDString</c> 參數識別之字串的長度。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the property of the accessible element to be annotated.
trans-unit.target: 指定要標註之可存取項目的屬性。

trans-unit.source: Specifies a new value for the property.
trans-unit.target: 指定屬性的新值。
